{"tid":1608681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講今日中国擺大壽 不如一齊睇下世界頭條講咩吖","createTime":"2019-10-01T11:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:21:05.000Z","uid":264709,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"17641b5fe5b8c40bec2ae684237b361541c04de5","tid":1608681,"uid":264709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:21:12.000Z","msg":"The Guardian 衛報<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>国慶示威加劇 香港示威者心口中槍</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">国慶報導得一小格</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyBvw8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyBvw8a.jpg&h=8529058e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBBC<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>閱兵過後 香港怒火燃燒</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">首頁無国慶報導</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5wCFUmx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5wCFUmx.jpg&h=49e8f3ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNew York Times<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港警察 国慶日槍擊示威者</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">首頁無国慶報導</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGe83eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGe83eR.jpg&h=f34e9431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCNN<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港暴力爆發 香港警察槍擊示威者</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">国慶同示威都有報</span><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZ8t3eQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZ8t3eQ.jpg&h=c5cab6d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nReuters路透社<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>国慶日香港街頭變戰場</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">首頁無国慶報導</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pf0Umw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pf0Umw.jpg&h=514b422a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六區開花手足中彈全世界睇住<br />\n香港人用血汗